original_title: The Marvellous Maggie Smith: A Celebration
overview: A look at Dame Maggie Smith's life from a two-up two-down in Essex to Broadway and Hollywood. Starring in more than 60 films and 70 plays across her 70-year career, Maggie's incredible determination and talent landed her among the elite.
title: The Marvellous Maggie Smith: A Celebration
